OL,3,CDirty nappies, cans and toys among
OL,4,Clitter left at award-winning beach
OL,6,FDirty nappies, cans, buckets and
OL,7,Fspades and takeaway boxes were among
OL,8,Fthe rubbish left on a beach in Dorset
OL,9,Ffollowing the hot weather at the
OL,10,Fweekend.
OL,12,FBins were left overflowing and rubbish
OL,13,Fwas strewn over the sand after many
OL,14,Fpeople flocked to Weymouth beach to
OL,15,Fsoak up the sun.
