OL,3,CDirty nappies, cans and toys among
OL,4,Clitter left at award-winning beach
OL,6,FA group looking to reduce sea and
OL,7,Fcoastal litter have posted pictures of
OL,8,Fthe rubbish they collected each
OL,9,Fevening, with the hopes of educating
OL,10,Fpeople on the importance of taking
OL,11,Fyour rubbish home and recycling.
OL,13,FThe said: "Some people as usual didn't
OL,14,Feven make the effort.
OL,16,F"Six sacks collected and sorted for
OL,17,Frecycling. 35 glass bottles, 105
OL,18,Fplastic bottles and glasses, 215 cans,
OL,19,Fa sack of toys, 3 inflatables and a
OL,20,Fbag of general waste including 3 used
OL,21,Fnappies."
