OL,6,FOn social media the group added:
OL,7,F"We've had an awful lot of press
OL,8,Fcoverage around the weekend's mess on
OL,9,Fthe beach, however most seem to want
OL,10,Fto concentrate on how lazy people are
OL,11,Fhowever the elephant in the room is
OL,12,Fthe amount of waste created."
OL,14,F"It costs #250,000 a year to clean the
OL,15,Fbeach mostly during the summer, less
OL,16,Fthan 10% is recycled.
