OL,4,Clitter left at award-winning beach
OL,6,F"We currently recycle 90% of OUR beach
OL,7,Fclean waste, we can recycle cans,
OL,8,Fplastic bottles, plastic toys, crab
OL,9,Flines, glass bottles & inflatables, it
OL,10,Fis possible if there is a will to do
OL,11,Fso.
OL,13,F"We need to cut down on waste and
OL,14,Frecycle more."
OL,16,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for
OL,17,FWeymouth Town Council said: "We are
OL,18,Fdisappointed to see so much litter
OL,19,Fleft behind after the sunny weekend.
