OL,3,CDirty nappies, cans and toys among
OL,4,Clitter left at award-winning beach
OL,6,F"There are plenty of bins provided
OL,7,Falong the seafront for proper disposal
OL,8,Fof litter, as well as recycling
OL,9,Ffacilities. Or people can take their
OL,10,Frubbish home with them, which also
OL,11,Fhelps to keep our award-winning beach
OL,12,Fclean.
OL,14,F"We also work with Weymouth and
OL,15,FPortland Marine Project and Dorset
OL,16,FFree Litter to provide a toy library
OL,17,Fso that people can reuse buckets and
OL,18,Fspades rather than buying more single
OL,19,Fuse plastics. These are open for all
OL,20,Fto use."
